Generic single-database configuration with an async-friendly sync DSN for migrations.

Setiap migrasi wajib:
- Ada `upgrade()` + `downgrade()` yang simetris.
- `server_default` untuk kolom non-nullable baru di tabel existing.
- Ditest lokal: `uv run alembic upgrade head` lalu `uv run alembic downgrade -1`.
